Author: grabameal
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GrabAmeal - AirBnB for Dinning poised to disrupt eating out industry
Body: GrabAmeal: a transparent way to explore quality food at reasonable price   Finding a good and comfortable accommodation or hiring a sharing cab is easier for an individual when you are away from home. But finding homemade tasty meal according to personal tang is a difficult task because meal sharing has not become that easily available today, rather finding the quality venue for meal sharing is not widely open till date unless you use GrabAmeal platform.  What is GrabAmeal?  GrabAmeal is the peer-to-peer network, which is empowered by blockchain. Due to blockchain integration, transaction on this food market platform is completely safe and transparent. Here food sellers (hosts) can contact buyers (guests) for service fresh homemade meal and buyers can buy quality foods at their discretion. It is an immaculate business opportunity for food sellers no doubt from home, it is a mega opening for food buyers wanting to buy homemade quality foods, which is hardly available.  How the buyers work here?  The buyers have to be profile conscious here because they need to open an account on blockchain so that they can access the hosts’ database by random search. The buyers can do their search area wise as well as food cuisine wise. The food can be brought at home, or a buyer can visit the host’s place to have the meal shared. This is a beautiful way to share meal, which is a great way to extend friend and acquaintances in completely a new city.  The review and rating system of GrabAmeal about food sellers is an additional resource for buyers in finalizing their hosts. Before ordering a meal to the shortlisted hosts, the buyer should check the business details of the buyer. GrabAmeal works like a filter where all sellers’ data can be viewed for buying homemade meals from him.  GAM wallet is the way to transact  Everybody can become a host on GrabAmeal: however you need to maintain a crypto-wallet with certain GAM token balance in it. There is no involvement of middle men and that makes the price always cheaper than food sold from quality hotels or inns. Once you have enjoyed the food at the seller’s place, you can review the cook for his culinary performance.  The buyers can join their hands in dispute resolution protocol of GAM. The contribution of casting vote will attract earning of GAM token, which is an additional benefit of the buyers for joining GrabAmeal platform for quality homemade food search and enjoying the same.  Want to know more exciting opportunity offered by GrabAmeal? GAM is offering their franchise opening all over the world. Author: grabameal
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GrabAmeal - AirBnB for Dinning poised to disrupt eating out industry
Body: GrabAmeal: A transparent business opportunity with great scope of earning   Meal sharing is an old global custom of showing hospitality to guests. The global marketplace of GrabAmeal offers a unique opportunity to convert this hospitality gesture into a successful blockchain empowered home-based business opportunity where everybody can be the host and share their culinary skill with food enthusiasts(buyers) for gratifying their passion for showing cooking skill and earning money by establishing a home based restaurant.  The business model of GrabAMeal  Starting business from home is a successful startup now. For example, AirBNB business module offers opportunity for setting home based rental home. Similarly GrabAmeal offers the opportunity of opening a home based restaurant where every homemaker, professional chef, or culinary enthusiasts can be the host (seller) and every food seeker (love to have homemade, fresh meal according to personal choice) can be the guest (buyer).  The host needs to open a profile on the GrabAMeal platform with all his business details and food type available for offer. Buyer should be able to get all his host’s details while searching for food online. The buyer should open his profile on the platform so that before accepting an online order, the sellers can check the buyers’ history.  All data and buyer and seller information will be stored in Blockchain so that none of them can be tampered. Both buyers and sellers can be reviewed depending on the quality and satisfaction level of business transaction.  The earning opportunity on GrabAMeal  The sellers can earn in two ways on GrabAmeal.  · The meal price will be paid by the buyer and it will paid online by GAM token.  · On the other hand, every food seller can join GAM in their dispute resolution protocol and can earn for their casting vote and helping in solving a business dispute.  The benefits of joining GrabAmeal as a seller (host)  · Excellent scope to start a home based business where the culinary enthusiasts can use their passion for cooking as their way of earning  · The scope of earning in decentralized cryptocurrency  · Having the scope to promote profile: higher the profile is, better is business volume.  · The seller will be able to review a buyer on his buying habit as well as on his transaction, etc.  GrabAmeal platform on blockchain is a wonderful opportunity to grow and earn amicably using your spare time from your home. Author: grabameal
Title: [ANN] [ICO] GrabAmeal - AirBnB for Dinning poised to disrupt eating out industry
Body: GrabAmeal: Meal Sharing For Connecting Diners around the World   GrabAMeal (GAM) is the global meal sharing platform, which is blockchain empowered and offers transparent opportunity for food buyers and sellers to transact with each other. Food enthusiasts looking for healthy and freshly prepared home cooked meal can contact GAM enlisted food sellers or online ordering of home cooked mail according to the type of food the cook is selling via his home based restaurants.  This is advantageous for food sellers as it is an opportunity for them to start a home based business based of their culinary skill and passion for haring meal with buyers.  For food buyers, GAM offers an opportunity to enjoy healthy home cooked food, no matter if they are away from their native home. The idea of meal sharing or the cooks on GAM is like sharing their culinary culture: often cooks call the buyers to have food in their home. It’s like booking a home on AirBNB, where you have to stay on someone’s place instead of staying at a hotel or guest house.  In other words like AirBNB home, GAM offers opportunity of having meal in AirBNB restaurants, where cooks are the hosts and buyers are the guests.  GrabAMeal (GAM) works like this: Hosts (cooks) creates a profile, describe what they’re cooking (food type), fix a price, and indicate their available time for sharing food. Guests find an online host at their nearby place and orders meal. If the host accepts, the two parties enjoy a meal together, and at the end of the transaction both of them can rate and review each others.  All the reviews get stored in GAM blockchain, which cannot be modified. This way, buyers can identify skilled and best hosts and hosts can assess a guest by checking his profile while accepting an online order.  According to GAM spokesperson, “People are turning to meal sharing network frequently as this peer-to-peer network helps in understanding and sharing a deeper cultural integrity while staying out of home”, and the integration with blockchain ensures complete food safety, security of transaction, and establishment of trust and transparency.  Besides, there are independent editors, who will help users in solving disputes if any.  All business transactions on GAM will be done by using GAM crypto-token. Both host and gust will have to maintain their GAM wallet and minimum GAM balance to complete a deal.  To know more about GrabAMeal world or if you have any questions, look them up in our website: https://grabameal.world/ico/ or  FAQ https://grabamealworld.freshdesk.com/support/home  or  send us a support ticket  https://grabamealworld.freshdesk.com/support/tickets/new  or  Feel free to email us at: contact@grabameal.world
